Introduction

Kim Gayoung, known under her stage name Zena, is a South Korean singer and rapper under THE MUZE Entertainment. She is best known as the main rapper, lead vocalist, visual and maknae of the girl group RESCENE.

She debuted as a member of the girl group RESCENE on March 26, 2024, with their single album "Re:Scene".

She was a contestant on "Stars Awakening".
